elements.name: Should be able to Close the schedule

steps.name: User navigates to 'lattice.url' page
User is at home screen after login with "username" and "password"
User clicks on 'Training Management' in navigation panel
User clicks on the 'Training Schedules' tab
User clicks on first available schedule record
User clicks on the 'Participants Planning' tab in training schedule page
User clicks on 'Include Participants' button in training Schedule page
User waits for 5 seconds
User selects the planned participants
User clicks on save button
User clicks on button 'Status Update'
User updates the training status to 'Scheduled'
User clicks on update button
User clicks on button 'Status Update'
User updates the training status to 'Active'
User clicks on update button
User clicks on the 'Actual Participants' tab in training schedule page
User clicks on 'Include Staff from Planned Participants' button in training Schedule page
User clicks on 'Include Staff From Others' button in training Schedule page
User clicks on button 'Status Update'
